00084 void NiftiArmNode::IMUCallback(const sensor_msgs::Imu::ConstPtr& msg) {

00086         counter++;
00087         if (!(counter % (IMU_PUB_RATE / 2))) {

00095                 #else
00096                   btMatrix3x3 matrix(q);

00099                 #endif
00100 
00101                 switch (canSettings.IMU_axis.c_str()[0]) {
00102                 case 'X':
00103                         //ROS_INFO("Using X-Axis");
00104                         IMU_angle = roll;
00105                         break;
00106                 case 'Z':
00107                         //ROS_INFO("Using Z-Axis");
00108                         IMU_angle = yaw;
00109                         break;
00110                 default:
00111                         //ROS_INFO("Using Y-Axis");
00112                         IMU_angle = pitch;
00113                         break;
00114                 }
00115                 if (canSettings.IMU_inverted) {
00116                         //ROS_INFO("Invert angle");
00117                         IMU_angle = -IMU_angle;
00118                 }
00119                 if (canSettings.setoffset) {
00120                         canSettings.IMU_angle_offset = IMU_angle;
00121                         canSettings.setoffset = false;
00122                 }
00123                 IMU_angle -= canSettings.IMU_angle_offset;
00124                 adoptPosition();
